&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Subaru Pacific is an innovative and highly respected leader in the automotive industry. We’re growing our team and looking for a motivated, persuasive, and customer-focused Service BDC Representative to join our Service Center.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;f yo&lt;/em&gt;u thrive on connecting with people, enjoy influencing customer decisions, and take pride in turning conversations into appointments — we want to hear from you.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Service BDC Representative, you’ll be the voice and first impression of our Service Department. Your role will focus on driving service business through proactive communication and persuasive follow-up:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Proactively reach out to customers to schedule and confirm service appointments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Brand Training: &lt;/strong&gt;You&#39;ll be trained to work with multiple vehicle brands so you can support different dealerships and help wherever needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Use sales and negotiation techniques to encourage customers to bring their vehicles in for maintenance, recalls, and repairs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Handle inbound and outbound calls, texts, and emails with a goal-oriented, customer-first mindset&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Overcome objections and present the value of timely service and genuine Subaru care&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Follow up with previous customers, missed appointments, and declined services to convert opportunities into booked appointments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely with Service Advisors and management to maximize daily shop capacity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Maintain detailed, accurate records and consistently meet or exceed service appointment goals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&lt;/strong&gt; Minimum of one year of experience in a call center, BDC, or high-volume customer contact role required (automotive experience preferred).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Proven sales or negotiation ability with a track record of meeting or exceeding performance targets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Exceptional communication, listening, and persuasion skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong organizational habits and attention to detail&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Energetic, upbeat, and professional attitude&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
